name: WhiteRainforSleep
0:
”Alexa open white rain”
”Alexa ask white rain to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: white rain
des:
Fall into a deep sleep with some white rain sounds. A perfect blend of white noise and rain drops falling, White Rain is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start White Rain, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
